title: Dolphins coach Joe Philbin fired 4 games into his 4th season
text: > Florida Dolphins coach Joe Philbin fired 4 games into his 4th season Former Miami Dolphins tight ends coach Dan Campbell gestures as he speaks during a news conference after being promoted to interim head coach, Monday, Oct. 5, 2015 in Davie, Fla. Joe Philbin has been fired four games into his fourth season as coach of the Dolphins, and one day after a flop on an international stage that helped to seal his fate. (AP Photo/Wilfredo Lee)
